subject: Dear Customer;
body:
Dear Customer;
Are you aware of your abandoned fund here in our Bank?
Kindly respond back for the claim of your fund.
Best Regards
Mr. Gbenga Shobo

subject: Re:   Dear Customer;
body:
Hello Mr. Gbenga Shobo,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I must admit, I wasn't aware of any abandoned fund in your bank. Could you please provide me with more details about this? How did this fund come to be abandoned and what is the process for claiming it?

I appreciate your assistance and look forward to hearing back from you.

Best wishes,
Marilyn
